Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,this is all I have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,what did you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1EF7F&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:15.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,why do you say？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:20.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,刃を砥ぐ、微睡む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:23.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,詩と快楽は未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:31.61,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,survive of vision
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.68,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,final white heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:42.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,さあ奪い合うよ傷を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:46.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why.
