Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.13,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不死树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:43.62,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8EACD&}何为真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:44.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,何为真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我将成为真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.63,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8EACD&}我将成为真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.18,0:00:59.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我看到那片光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8EACD&}这就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.89,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,这就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:09.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE8EACD&}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:15.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你为什么说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:20.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,磨刀 小憩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:23.77,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,生存之景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,诗和快乐是未来
