Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:31.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我迷失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,生存之景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:38.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,未完成的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:42.33,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,互相争夺伤痛
